        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Grid Hardening Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill expands the Smart Grid Investment Matching Grant Program within the Department of Energy to include grants for technology, equipment, or hardening measures that enable the electric grid to better withstand the effects of extreme weather, a wildfire, or any other natural disaster.</p>]]>
        </text>
